    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>In this South African phase 1/2b study, we demonstrated vaccine efficacy (VE) of two doses of AZD1222 for asymptomatic and symptomatic SARS-CoV-2 infection: 90.6% against wild-type and 77.1% against the Delta variant \u22659 months after vaccination. VE against infection with the Beta variant, which preceded circulation of Delta, was 6.7%.</jats:p>\n                <jats:sec>\n                  <jats:title>Clinical trial identifier</jats:title>\n                  <jats:p>\n                    <jats:ext-link xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" ext-link-type=\"uri\" xlink:href=\"http://CT.gov\">CT.gov</jats:ext-link>\n                    <jats:ext-link xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" ext-link-type=\"clintrialgov\" xlink:href=\"NCT04444674\">NCT04444674</jats:ext-link>\n                  </jats:p>\n                </jats:sec>",
